  "texts": [
    "The rest of this article is structured as follows: Section 2 summarizes and categorizes the relevant literature pertaining to MS-RCPSP based on several dimensions.",
    "Section 3 explains the structured research methodology used and presents some statistical analysis.",
    "Section 4 reports the results of the bibliometric analysis, while Section 5 reports the results of the network analysis.",
    "Finally, in Section 6, the paper concludes by providing a summary of the main findings and identifying promising areas for future research based on the identified gaps along with useful insights for project managers.",
    "This literature review is divided into four sections, with each focusing on different aspects of the MS-RCPSP."
  ]
}